---
import LineShot from "../../components/assets/LineShot.astro";
---

<section
  class="pt-10 bg-color-secondary rounded-t-[60px] rounded-b-none border-t border-color box-shadow"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[668px]">
    <p
      class="text-3xl leading-9 letter-spacing-[-0.75px] font-medium text-color px-2 sm:px-6 fade-in-scroll"
    >
      Centralized Compliance Repository
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[668px] px-2 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center gap-4">
      <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 fade-in-scroll">
        Openlane functions as a comprehensive, centralized repository for all
        compliance-related materials. This includes a wide range of documents
        such as regulatory requirements, internal policies, standard operating
        procedures, and industry best practices. By consolidating these
        resources into a single, easily accessible platform, Openlane eliminates
        the need for scattered documents and disparate systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[668px] mt-10">
    <p
      class="text-3xl leading-9 letter-spacing-[-0.75px] font-medium text-color px-2 sm:px-6 fade-in-scroll"
    >
      Dynamic Compliance Tracking and Monitoring
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[668px] px-2 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center gap-4">
      <p class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 fade-in-scroll">
        Openlane goes beyond simply storing documents; it provides dynamic
        tracking and monitoring capabilities that enable users to actively
        manage compliance status. The platform allows for the creation of
        customized compliance checklists and workflows, ensuring that all
        necessary steps are completed and documented. Users can track the
        progress of each task, identify potential bottlenecks, and receive
        automated alerts for upcoming deadlines or overdue items.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-asset z-[1]">
    <div
      class="relative max-w-[1071px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 md:gap-12 items-stretch mt-10 z-[1] pb-10"
    >
      <div class="lg:col-span-12 flex justify-center pt-[50px] px-2 sm:px-6">
        <p
          class="font-medium tracking-[-0.9px] text-4xl text-center mb-4 md:mb-0 fade-in-scroll"
        >
          Effortless, End-to-End Compliance Management
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 z-[-1] w-full h-full pointer-events-none hidden lg:block opacity-40 fade-in-scroll"
      >
        <LineShot class="w-full h-auto" />
      </div>

      <div
        class="lg:col-span-6 h-full flex flex-col max-w-[400px] px-6 md:px-2"
      >
        <p
          class="font-medium text-3xl leading-9 tracking-[-0.75px] mb-2 sm:mb-4 fade-in-scroll"
        >
          Streamline Compliance Management
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 md:mb-6 tracking-[-0.6px] fade-in-scroll"
        >
          Openlane streamlines compliance management by providing real-time
          visibility into control status and facilitating efficient task
          assignment. Monitor implementation progress, track evidence collection
          status, and manage control testing schedules all in one place. Users
          can easily assign specific compliance tasks to individuals or teams,
          setting clear deadlines and providing detailed instructions. The
          platform's integrated workflow engine automates the routing of tasks,
          ensuring that they are completed in a timely and consistent manner.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex justify-center items-center h-full">
        <div
          class="framework-image-container w-full flex justify-center items-center !h-[400px]"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/control-report.png"
            alt="Control Report"
            class="max-h-[400px] w-auto object-contain rounded-xl z-[1] zoom-img fade-in-scroll"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="lg:col-span-6 h-full flex flex-col max-w-[400px] px-6 md:px-2"
      >
        <p
          class="font-medium text-3xl leading-9 tracking-[-0.75px] mb-2 sm:mb-4 fade-in-scroll"
        >
          Control Mapping and Reporting
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-lg font-normal leading-7 mb-6 tracking-[-0.6px] fade-in-scroll"
        >
          Openlane's control mapping and reporting features empower
          organizations to efficiently manage compliance across multiple
          frameworks. By mapping controls between standards like SOC 2, ISO
          27001, and NIST 800-53, you eliminate redundant work and ensure that
          evidence collected for one framework can be leveraged for others. This
          cross-framework visibility not only reduces manual effort, but also
          accelerates your path to assessing new market opportunities.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex justify-center items-center h-full">
        <div class="framework-image-container !h-[300px]">
          <img
            src="/assets/framework-report.png"
            alt="Framework Report"
            class="!h-[300px] w-auto object-contain rounded-xl shadow-lg z-[1] zoom-img fade-in-scroll"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
